(294, 161, 2, 'Final notice of opening Algebra B2 class (TTH004) for students who still owe the subject', '<p>Final notice of opening Algebra B2 class (TTH004) for students who still owe this subject<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>NOTIFICATION</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Re: Opening the class of Algebra B2 for the first semester of the school year 2018-2019</p>\r\n\r\n<p>for regular University students</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Based on the previous K2015 training program and training programs from K2016 in the fields of Electronics - Telecommunications, Physics, Nuclear Engineering;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Based on the proposal of Faculty of Physics - Technical Physics;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Training Department announces to all students of the regular university system the majors of Electronic and Telecommunications Engineering, Physics, and Nuclear Engineering from the 2015 Recruitment or earlier about opening classes to re-study the University. No. B2 (TTH004) in the first semester of 2018-2019 at Nguyen Van Cu campus as follows:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Registration time:<br />\r\n- From September 20, 2018 to the end of September 24, 2018.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Place of registration:<br />\r\n- Department of Grassroots Training Nguyen Van Cu</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Registration conditions<br />\r\n- Regular university students in the fields of Electronics and Telecommunication, Physics, and Nuclear Engineering from 2015 and earlier have not yet completed the Algebra B2 module (TTH004).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>School schedule:<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;- Starting week: September 24, 2018.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>No.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>HP code</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Course name</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Class code</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Schedule</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Classroom</p>\r\n\r\n<p>first</p>\r\n\r\n<p>TTH004</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Algebra B2</p>\r\n\r\n<p>15_L1</p>\r\n\r\n<p>T4, 17h50 - 21h</p>\r\n\r\n<p>F303</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Note:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;Students who have registered at the Department of Physics - Technical Physics (attached file) do not need to register again, the University has entered the list into open classes for students.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"width:595px\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>STT</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>MSSV</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Họ v&agrave; t&ecirc;n sinh vi&ecirc;n</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Ng&agrave;nh học</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Ghi ch&uacute;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>1&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>1413015</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Huỳnh Nguyễn Kh&aacute;nh Ch&acirc;u</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Vật l&yacute; học</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>2&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>1413100</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Nguyễn Hữu Nghĩa</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Vật l&yacute; học</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>3&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>1420021</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Huỳnh Thanh Duy</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Điện tử viễn th&ocirc;ng</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>1420041</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Cao Th&aacute;i Hiệp</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Điện tử viễn th&ocirc;ng</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\r